Additionally, the paper discusses the effect of quantization on the loss landscape, which is a key concept in machine learning optimization. 

The paper also touches on computer vision (cs.CV) as it discusses the accuracy of quantization methods for image classification tasks. 

Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is another likely sub-category as the paper deals with optimizing neural networks, which is a key area of research in AI. 

Neural networks (cs.NE) is also a possible sub-category as the paper focuses on quantizing the parameters of neural networks. 

Finally, augmented reality (cs.AR) is a less likely sub-category as the paper does not explicitly discuss AR, but it is possible that the quantization techniques discussed in the paper could be applied to AR applications.
